1. init npm init
2. Installation  npm install cypress --save-dev
3. Open  npx cypress open

Format lines: option + may + F


Install plugin for use xpath: https://www.npmjs.com/package/cypress-xpath

config:
https://docs.cypress.io/guides/references/configuration
https://docs.cypress.io/api/cypress-api/config#Arguments

usando consola:
https://docs.cypress.io/guides/guides/command-line#Installation
node_modules/.bin/cypress run  //ejecuta todos los test que tengas, al final te saca un cuadro con un report. Ejecucion headless

npx cypress run --headed  //fuerza a levantar navegador

npx cypress run --spec "cypress/e2e/1-getting-started/Asserts.cy.js"  //Ejecutar un test concreto
npx cypress run --spec "cypress/e2e/1-getting-started/*"  //Ejecutar todos los test en un spec

